title: Proposal to Boost the BMON-BNB farm and a New Syrup Pool
body:
#### PancakeSwap Welcomes Binamon to Syrup Pool!

CAKE holders, today we are happy to be able to offer you a new Syrup Pool from **Binamon**, a complete metaverse of Digital Monsters that live on the Binance Smart Chain.

#### What is Boost?

Boost is basically an increase in farm multiplier over a set period of time, which is offered in exchange for additional tokens from the boosted project, which are then put into a new Syrup Pool!

So basically, the BMON-BNB farm will go to a 1x multiple for 48 hours, then 0.5x thereafter. Don’t worry, this will only cause temporary dilution among the other farms. At the same time, there will be a new BMON Syrup Pool with 3,500,000 BMON tokens to be earned by staking CAKE.

#### The Syrup Pool:

Stake CAKE tokens to earn BMON tokens!

-   **Total Tokens:** 3,500,000 BMON
-   **Distribution duration:** 60 days
-   **Start block:** #12162570 *[(approx. 11am UTC on October 28th 2021)](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/12162570)*
-   **Finish block:** #13890570 *[(approx. 11am UTC on December 27th 2021)](https://www.bscscan.com/block/countdown/13890570)*
-   **Token rewards per block:** 2.0254 BMON

#### Max Stake per wallet:

100 CAKE for the first 48 hours, then unlimited CAKE staking afterwards.

To give as many CAKE holders the opportunity to Farm some Sryup pool rewards at a high APY, we will have a 100 CAKE token cap staking limit per user for the first 48 hours.

#### What is BINAMON?

From the team: “Binamon is a complete metaverse of Digital Monsters that live on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC), which allows millions of people to join the NFT & blockchain-based gaming world in an easy, creative and fun way.

Through a smart contract called Booster, Binamon NFTs will be minted (BEP721), using the BMON token (BEP-20). The strength and powers of the NFTs are created randomly following probability calculations. Then the smart contract mints 3 different Binamons with unique features and powers.

BATTLE MODE: With the battle mode, users will be able to fight each other by wagering BMON tokens. The winner will take the prize.

MULTIPLAYER GAME: An adventure multiplayer game, whose economy will be powered by the BMON token.”

#### To learn more about Binamon, the chefs advise you to visit their official communication channels:

- **Website**: [*https://binamon.org/*](https://binamon.org/)
- **Twitter**: [*https://twitter.com/binamonok*](https://twitter.com/binamonok)
- **Telegram**: [*https://t.me/binamon*](https://t.me/binamon)
- **Discord**: [*https://discord.gg/binamon*](https://discord.gg/binamon)
    
#### How do you stake CAKE to earn BMON rewards?

Follow this guide to staking in Syrup Pools:

[*https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide*](https://docs.pancakeswap.finance/products/syrup-pool/syrup-pool-guide)

#### BEWARE OF FOOD POISONING! ⚠️⚠️⚠️💀

The official BMON token contract address on Binance Smart Chain is:

*https://bscscan.com/token/0x08ba0619b1e7A582E0BCe5BBE9843322C954C340*

Any other BMON token will be a scam and will result in a financial loss. Always verify the token address before purchasing tokens. If you receive a BMON token airdrop from another address, it’s probably a scam and we advise you to ignore them.
